text: Afriansyah (born April 26, 1991), is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays as a forward for Liga 2 club Muba BaBel United. ==Career== He was signed for Muba BaBel United to played in Liga 2 on 2019 season. == Honours == === Club === Semen Padang * Liga 2 runner-up: 2018 ==References== == External links == * Afriansyah at Liga Indonesia * Afriansyah at Soccerway Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Semen Padang F.C. players Category:BaBel United F.C. players Category:Cilegon United players Category:Persita Tangerang players
